        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Renewable Chemicals Act of 2024&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill allows a new tax credit for the production of renewable chemicals. Specifically, it allows a credit for u p to 15% of the sales price of each pound of a renewable chemical. A renewable chemical is any chemical that is produced in the United States from renewable biomass and is not less than 95% biobased content.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The bill also allows a 30% tax credit for investment in renewable chemical production facilities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
